{"id":"moseroth","term":"Moseroth","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Bonds, one of the stations in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:30\">Num. 33:30</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:31\">31</a>), probably the same as Mosera.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:30","Numbers 33:31"]}